<!-- Section 2 — Opening -->
<section class="section-opening">
  <div class="container">
    <p class="section-opening__lead">Almost Human Group is a 501(c)(4) that fights for children, teens, and young adults aged 14-26. The ones foster care forgot. The ones schools failed. The ones nobody asked.</p>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 3 — Founder Story -->
<section class="section-founder" id="founder">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-founder__grid">
      <div class="section-founder__image">
        <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507003211169-0a1dd7228f2d?auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" alt="Founder portrait" loading="lazy">
      </div>
      <div class="section-founder__content">
        <span class="section-founder__label">THE FOUNDER</span>
        <h2 class="section-founder__headline">Aged Out. Built This.</h2>
        <p>Adopted at six. New home, new name. Every system after that treated him like a file folder. Foster care. Public school. Mental health intake. All built around young people. None built with them.</p>
        <p>The mental health crisis came. The mandate came with it: somebody has to build the thing that doesn't exist. Not another program that asks kids to be grateful for systems that fail them. An organization that puts them in charge of rewriting those systems entirely.</p>
        <p>That's AHG. Born from one person being tired of almost being seen, almost being heard, almost being treated as human in rooms that decided his future without knowing his name.</p>
        <blockquote class="section-founder__quote">
          <p>"Children are not at the will of the education system. The education system is at the will of the children."</p>
        </blockquote>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 4 — Mission -->
<section class="section-mission" id="mission">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="section-mission__inner">
      <span class="section-mission__label">OUR MISSION</span>
      <h2 class="section-mission__headline">The Uncompromising Voice of the Next Generation.</h2>
      <p>We build programs, shape policy, and demand seats at tables for children, teens, and young adults. Especially the ones in foster care, under-resourced schools, and broken systems. We do not wait. We do not ask nicely. We show up and we do not leave.</p>
      <div class="section-mission__structure">
        <h3>Why a 501(c)(4)?</h3>
        <p>Because these problems are political. A 501(c)(3) can serve food. A 501(c)(4) can serve food <em>and</em> go to the statehouse. We lobby. We endorse policy. We hold elected officials accountable by name. That's the point.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- Section 5 — Values -->
<section class="section-values" id="values">
  <div class="container">
    <span class="section-values__label">OUR VALUES</span>
    <h2 class="section-values__headline">Non-Negotiable.</h2>
    <div class="card-grid card-grid--five">
      <div class="card card--value">
        <span class="card__number">01</span>
        <h3 class="card__title">Proximity Over Distance</h3>
        <p class="card__text">People closest to the problem build the solution. Period.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card--value">
        <span class="card__number">02</span>
        <h3 class="card__title">Certainty Over Comfort</h3>
        <p class="card__text">We say what we mean. Vagueness is a luxury these kids can't afford.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card--value">
        <span class="card__number">03</span>
        <h3 class="card__title">Structure Over Symbolism</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Marches fade. Infrastructure stays. We build things that outlast us.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card--value">
        <span class="card__number">04</span>
        <h3 class="card__title">Urgency Without Chaos</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Fast because lives depend on it. Precise because sloppy work kills movements.</p>
      </div>
      <div class="card card--value">
        <span class="card__number">05</span>
        <h3 class="card__title">Accountability by Name</h3>
        <p class="card__text">Systems don't fail. People in charge of systems fail. We name them.</p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

